    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Drive away in a vehicle that\u2019s ready for its next chapter! This car is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for anyone looking for a solid ride at a great price. While it shows some honest wear from its time on the road and could use a little cosmetic attention, it remains a functional and spirited companion for your daily commutes!",
