    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior remains in factory-new condition with no signs of wear. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, making this an exceptional find for any collector or enthusiast seeking a pristine example.",
